            "title": "巨子生物折讓9.5%配股   低開近7.7%後跌幅收窄",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">巨子生物(02367)以每股66.65元作價，配售3500萬股，配股價較昨天收市價73.65元折讓9.5%，今早競價時段低開7.67%，報68元，現跌幅收窄至4.75%，報70.15元，成交27.73億元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"巨子生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/02367.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"巨子生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/02367.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">巨子生物官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">公司稱，配股集資淨額預期合共約為22.94億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">配售及認購所得款項淨額擬用於(i核心業務的發展及生態圈佈局，包括但不限於品牌推廣、市場營銷、品類擴展、海外業務及研發投入；及補充流動資金及作一般企業用途。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14860972-%e5%b7%a8%e5%ad%90%e7%94%9f%e7%89%a9%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%939-5%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1-%e4%bd%8e%e9%96%8b%e8%bf%917-7%e5%be%8c%e8%b7%8c%e5%b9%85%e6%94%b6%e7%aa%84",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20240517_FI_source-web_02367-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 09:40:55",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "路勁屯門新盤推75伙  售價325.25萬起",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14859351&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">路勁地產牽頭發展的屯門管翠路新盤凱和山已屆現樓，推出全新價單第5號，合共75伙，折實售價325.25萬至537.16萬元，折實呎價7908元至9928元，折實平均呎價約9080元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">路勁地產銷售及市場推廣總監顏景鳳表示，加推單位實用面積381至587方呎；除了現有的2種付款計劃，分別為「120天極靈活付款辦法」、「360天現金優惠付款辦法」及「首18個月免息免供80%第一按揭貸款」外，現推出「90天Chill級付款辦法」，連同其他折扣優惠最高折扣達36%。部署短期內上載銷售安排，有機會於復活節假期內開售。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14859351-%e8%b7%af%e5%8b%81%e5%b1%af%e9%96%80%e6%96%b0%e7%9b%a4%e6%8e%a875%e4%bc%99-%e5%94%ae%e5%83%b9325-25%e8%90%ac%e8%b5%b7",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/10/pp_new-flat-transaction_fb.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 09:36:02",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港灣豪庭2房538萬成交   持貨15年升值五成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14859306&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美聯物業奧運站分行新近促成一宗大角咀港灣豪庭2房戶的二手成交，上車客以538萬元承接，2011年貨升值約5成。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">該行指，上述成交的單位為大角咀港灣豪庭1座低層E室，實用面積約337平方呎，屬2房間隔。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">據悉，單位以544萬元放盤，略議價後以538萬元承接單位自住，折合實用呎價約15,964元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">參考成交資料，原業主於2011年11月以約358萬元購入上述物業，持貨約14年，是次轉手帳賺約180萬元，或約50.3%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14859306-%e6%b8%af%e7%81%a3%e8%b1%aa%e5%ba%ad2%e6%88%bf538%e8%90%ac%e6%88%90%e4%ba%a4-%e6%8c%81%e8%b2%a815%e5%b9%b4%e5%8d%87%e5%80%bc%e4%ba%94%e6%88%90",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 09:36:04",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "元朗區溱柏4房套728萬元沽 創入伙後新低",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<iframe allowtransparency=\"true\" attrmap=\"{data-gtm-yt-inspected-10=true}\" src=\"https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article-audio?postId=14859291&amp;cantoneseUrl=&amp;mandarinUrl=\" style=\"border:none;overflow:hidden;position:relative;margin:0;width: 100%;height: 80px;padding-top: 10px;\"></iframe>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中原地產元朗分行表示，元朗區本月上半月錄得約61宗二手買賣成交，與上月同期62宗相若中</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">其中溱柏6座低層A室，實用面積958平方呎，四房套房間隔，開價830萬元連車位放售，現以728萬元不連車位沽出，造價創屋苑同類單位入伙後新低，折合實用呎價7599元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">原業主於2015年3月以904.6萬元連車位一手買入，持貨10年，帳面蝕176.6萬元或20%，但車位現時市值大約140萬元，如成功沽出，相信蝕幅將會大幅收窄。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14859291-%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e5%8d%80%e6%ba%b1%e6%9f%8f4%e6%88%bf%e5%a5%97728%e8%90%ac%e5%85%83%e6%b2%bd-%e5%89%b5%e5%85%a5%e4%bc%99%e5%be%8c%e6%96%b0%e4%bd%8e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240726_PP_TRANSACTION_BP_FB.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 09:36:06",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指開市跌4點 深成指跌59點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段偏軟，上證綜指以3261點開市，跌14點或0.44%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報9715點，亦跌59點或0.61%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數跌17點或0.47%，開報3755點；創業板指數開市報1893點，跌14點或0.74%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14860965-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e8%b7%8c4%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e8%b7%8c59%e9%bb%9e",
