        {
            "title": "中國2月增持235億美元美國國債",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中國2月增持美國國債，增加235億美元，大於1 月的18億美元，持倉規模達去年1 月以來新高，僅次於日本。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美國國債。\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美國國債。\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2024/01/20240103_BLOG_-5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美國國債。</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國財政部公布，持有美國國債最多的海外國為日本，2 月再增持466億美元，同樣大於1 月增持的195億美元，持有增至11259萬億美元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">英國2 月增持101億美元，至7503億美元，排名第三。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國國債上周創2001年以來最大單周跌幅，前財長耶倫表示，不認為中國會拋售美債，因為會令人民幣升值，損害其本身利益。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14860955-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b2%e6%9c%88%e5%a2%9e%e6%8c%81235%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e7%be%8e%e5%9c%8b%e5%9c%8b%e5%82%b5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/../blogger/2025/04/20241230_FI_source-ap_US_China_Hack.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 09:35:59",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段變動不大 恒指微升9點報21066點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">華爾街股市昨晚再度急挫，但未影響亞洲主要股市今早表現，港股亦於競價時段變動不大。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/20250311_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生指數開市報21066點，升9點或0.05%。恒生科技指數開報4790點，跌5點或0.12%；國企指數以7776點開市，跌2點或0.03%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股互有升跌，阿里巴巴(09988)開報105.1元，跌0.29%；騰訊(00700)開報450.4元，升0.54%；美團(03690)開報133.2元，跌1.26%。滙控(00005)開報80.1元，升0.69%；友邦(01299)開報53.15元，升0.76%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240826_FI_source-web_03690-GW-1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">金山雲(03896)發美國存託股及新股集資，該股今早開市應聲跌7.36%，報5.92元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">卓悅控股(00653)擬1供3集資，該股今早開報0.101元，跌6.48%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滿貫集團(03390)大股東持有部份股份昨天被斬倉，該股今早復牌於競價時段反彈30%，報0.39元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14860958-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e8%ae%8a%e5%8b%95%e4%b8%8d%e5%a4%a7-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%be%ae%e5%8d%879%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b121066%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20240420240415_FI_source-web_HKSTOCK.png.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-17 09:31:04",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "即月期指開報21150點 高水93點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報21150點，跌79點，較上日現貨收市價21056點高水93點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報4820點，跌34點，高水24點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報7818點，跌15點，高水39點。</p>\n</div>",
